<document xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/XDOC/2.0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
  xsi:schemaLocation="http://maven.apache.org/XDOC/2.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/xdoc-2.0.xsd">

  <properties>
    <title>Home</title>
    <author email="dev@onami.apache.org">Apache Onami Documentation Team</author>
  </properties>

  <body>
    <section name="Welcome to Apache Onami!" class="hero-unit">
      <p><span style="font-weight: bold">Apache Onami</span> is a project focused on the development and
      maintenance of a set of Google Guice extensions not provided out of the box by the library itself nor the
      Google developers team, such as integration with 3rd part frameworks or extra functionalities.</p>

      <p>The name takes inspiration from <a href="http://www.101zenstories.com/index.php?story=8">Great Waves</a>
      (<i>O-nami</i>, in Japanese) Zen story.</p>
    </section>

    <div id="components" class="carousel slide">
      <!-- Carousel items -->
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="active item">
          <div class="hero-unit">
            <h1>Guava</h1>
            <p>Google Guice integration modules for Google Guava.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-primary pull-right" href="./guava">Learn more</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <div class="hero-unit">
            <h1>Scheduler</h1>
            <p><a href="http://quartz-scheduler.org/">Quartz-Scheduler</a> integration.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-primary pull-right" href="./scheduler">Learn more</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <div class="hero-unit">
            <h1>SPI</h1>
            <p>A Java5 compatible small collection of reusable tools to make easier the integration with the
              <a href="http://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/sound/SPI-intro.html">Service Provider Interface</a> pattern.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-primary pull-right" href="./spi">Learn more</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <div class="hero-unit">
            <h1>Test</h1>
            <p>Simple library to inject <a href="http://www.junit.org/">Junit4</a> test classes via Google-Guice.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-primary pull-right" href="./test">Learn more</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <div class="hero-unit">
            <h1>Lifecycle</h1>
            <p><code>@AfterInjection</code> and <code>@Dispose</code> Guice annotations handlers</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-primary pull-right" href="./lyfecycle">Learn more</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <div class="hero-unit">
            <h1>Configuration</h1>
            <p>Expanded properties for Google Guice.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-primary pull-right" href="./configuration">Learn more</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <div class="hero-unit">
            <h1>Logging</h1>
            <p>Simple Logging Injector.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-primary pull-right" href="./logging">Learn more</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <div class="hero-unit">
            <h1>Cache</h1>
            <p><a href="http://jcp.org/en/jsr/detail?id=107">JSR107</a> annotations/handlers implementations.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-primary pull-right" href="./cache">Learn more</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <div class="hero-unit">
            <h1>Autobind</h1>
            <p>Guice Automatic Binding</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-primary pull-right" href="./autobind">Learn more</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <div class="hero-unit">
            <h1>Converters</h1>
            <p>Auxiliary <code>TypeConverter</code> implementations</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-primary pull-right" href="./converters">Learn more</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <div class="hero-unit">
            <h1>Validation</h1>
            <p>JSR303 (Bean Validation) integration extension for Google Guice</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-primary pull-right" href="./validation">Learn more</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <div class="hero-unit">
            <h1>Scopes</h1>
            <p>Auxiliary useful Google Guice Scopes</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-primary pull-right" href="./scopes">Learn more</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
          <div class="hero-unit">
            <h1>Persist</h1>
            <p>Extension for JPA and JTA</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-primary pull-right" href="./persist">Learn more</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section name="Artifacts" class="alert alert-info">
      <p>Looking for artifacts to manage with your preferred Dependencies resolver?
      Just browse Onami on <a href="http://search.maven.org/#search%7Cga%7C1%7Corg.apache.onami">Central repository</a>!</p>
    </section>

